{"tid":627730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又入波）休班警藏毒罪成還押","createTime":"2018-04-13T08:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T09:10:00.000Z","uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a735ba31f71502811056697934c01a29ca2d86ff","tid":627730,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"休班警藏毒罪成還押　官索戒毒所報告候判<br />\n<br />\n04月13日(五) 10:38<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/photo/bkn-20180413103859836-0413_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180413110108\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180413103859836-0413_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180413110108&h=1b70614f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oEdv9iYt8fcig2Xg4/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oEdv9iYt8fcig2Xg4%2Fgiphy.gif&h=22345504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隸屬刑事偵緝隊的男高級警員，於前年10月休班時在荃灣街頭被刑事情報科同袍截停，搜身時揭發他涉嫌在褲袋藏有俗稱「K仔」的毒品氯胺酮。涉案休班警潘俊東被控一項藏毒罪早前受審，今(13日)在西九龍法院被裁定罪成，裁判官決定先為他索取戒毒所報告，押後至本月27日判刑，期間被告還押。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官裁決時指，辯方主要辯稱渉案毒品並非從被告的長褲褲袋中發現，並稱現場閉路電視片段顯示其中一名警員在制服過程中，曾蹲在地上執起東西並打開內裏的疑似毒品。裁判官不同意辯方的說法，因閉路電視片段沒有顯示該警員曾打開物品，與該警員的證供並無違背，而據該警員的證供，他當時只是從地上拾起被告掉下的紙袋及被告的電話。裁判官認為該警員和其他控方證人的證供皆誠實可靠，故接納為事實。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官又指，對於被告供稱他當天所穿長褲的褲袋有破洞，不可能藏毒，辯方並曾呈上該褲作證物。惟裁判官指出，該長褲並非現場檢取作證物，而是事隔一年半才被列為證物，因此不代表該褲於案發時褲袋已有破洞。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於被告辯稱因在現場附近會見線人，才會現身現場，裁判官並不接納，因被告只能交出事發前該線人交出的情報作證明，與本案無關。而被告的職責不包括主動搜集情報，他接觸線人前又沒有通知上司，渉及違反警方規定，裁判官認為被告證供不合理且不可信，並相信被告是明知而藏有毒品，故裁定他藏毒罪成立。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，被告加入警隊21年，已婚，冀法庭考慮只渉及小量毒品，並非用作販賣，可獲法庭輕判。裁判官考慮案件渉及藏毒，故先為被告索閱戒毒所報告才作判刑。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"c99d0a0e3f4dc1c9d3f7b6af10ea1da22b7f9ef9","tid":627730,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"阿sir平時著穿窿褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000b8ea7c1bbdfce43837de21a4468da9d3d934c","tid":627730,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"竟然冇SHOW PASS/SHOW左都照搜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667c6bad9bfa23a172485667c390fb3c60d30c72","tid":627730,"uid":99568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/163104_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F163104_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=5e16fac6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65429d14ac1201b3b846a8ca75dfd963dc06dc03","tid":627730,"uid":143151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"個樣好mk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5068dbc21582dab58547b4989435cd3b875c426c","tid":627730,"uid":177342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"因為量少就要輕判?<br />\n毒品來架....你估麵粉呀?"},{"pid":"f409bd8a64f594efc9cccf4a79f4381667d6b9d4","tid":627730,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"做足審查咪一樣"},{"pid":"7f0a6effb33bed821bdca435c10de10516316938","tid":627730,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65429d14ac1201b3b846a8ca75dfd963dc06dc03","tid":627730,"uid":143151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"個樣好mk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy